{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 01 - EDA（探索的データ分析）\n",
    "\n",
    "## このノートブックの目的\n",
    "\n",
    "モデルを作る前に、**データを徹底的に理解する**ことが Kaggle では最も重要なステップです。\n",
    "\n",
    "EDA（Exploratory Data Analysis）で確認すること:\n",
    "1. データの形状・型・欠損値\n",
    "2. ターゲット（目的変数）の分布\n",
    "3. 数値変数の分布と外れ値\n",
    "4. カテゴリ変数の分布とターゲットとの関係\n",
    "5. 特徴量間の相関\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### このコンペの概要\n",
    "- **タスク**: 心疾患の有無を予測する 2 値分類\n",
    "- **評価指標**: ROC AUC（高いほど良い）\n",
    "- **ターゲット列**: `Heart Disease`\n",
    "- **データ**: `data/raw/train.csv`, `data/raw/test.csv`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 0. セットアップ"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import sys\n",
    "from pathlib import Path\n",
    "\n",
    "# プロジェクトルートを Python パスに追加（src.* を import するため）\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, str(Path.cwd().parent))\n",
    "\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "\n",
    "from src.config import DATA_RAW_DIR, TARGET_COL, FEATURE_NAMES, CATEGORICAL_LIKE\n",
    "from src.data import load_train_test\n",
    "\n",
    "# グラフのスタイル設定\n",
    "sns.set_theme(style=\"whitegrid\", palette=\"muted\")\n",
    "plt.rcParams[\"figure.figsize\"] = (10, 4)\n",
    "plt.rcParams[\"figure.dpi\"] = 100\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"セットアップ完了\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. データ読み込み"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "train, test, sub = load_train_test(data_dir=DATA_RAW_DIR, optimize=False)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Train shape: {train.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Test shape:  {test.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Sub shape:   {sub.shape}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 先頭5行を確認\n",
    "train.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 各列のデータ型を確認\n",
    "# object 型があれば文字列（カテゴリ）、int64/float64 が数値\n",
    "train.dtypes"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 欠損値の確認\n",
    "\n",
    "欠損値（NaN）がある場合、モデルに渡す前に補完する必要があります。\n",
    "- 数値列 → 中央値で補完（外れ値の影響を受けにくい）\n",
    "- カテゴリ列 → 最頻値で補完"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 欠損値の数と割合\n",
    "missing = train.isnull().sum()\n",
    "missing_pct = (missing / len(train) * 100).round(2)\n",
    "\n",
    "missing_df = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "    \"欠損数\": missing,\n",
    "    \"欠損率(%)\": missing_pct,\n",
    "}).query(\"欠損数 > 0\")\n",
    "\n",
    "if missing_df.empty:\n",
    "    print(\"欠損値なし！\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    display(missing_df)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ヒートマップで欠損パターンを可視化（欠損が少量のとき）\n",
    "if train.isnull().any().any():\n",
    "    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 3))\n",
    "    sns.heatmap(train.isnull().T, cbar=False, ax=ax, cmap=\"viridis\")\n",
    "    ax.set_title(\"欠損値マップ（黄色 = 欠損）\")\n",
    "    plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print(\"全列で欠損なし\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. ターゲット変数の分布\n",
    "\n",
    "**なぜ重要か?**\n",
    "- クラスが極端に偏っている（不均衡データ）と、モデルが多数派クラスだけを予測するようになる\n",
    "- 今回の評価指標 ROC AUC はある程度不均衡に強いが、確認しておくことが重要"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "target_counts = train[TARGET_COL].value_counts()\n",
    "target_pct = train[TARGET_COL].value_counts(normalize=True) * 100\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"ターゲット分布:\")\n",
    "for val in target_counts.index:\n",
    "    print(f\"  {val}: {target_counts[val]:,} 件 ({target_pct[val]:.1f}%)\")\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(10, 4))\n",
    "\n",
    "target_counts.plot(kind=\"bar\", ax=axes[0], color=[\"steelblue\", \"tomato\"], edgecolor=\"white\")\n",
    "axes[0].set_title(f\"{TARGET_COL} の件数\")\n",
    "axes[0].set_xlabel(\"\")\n",
    "axes[0].tick_params(axis=\"x\", rotation=0)\n",
    "\n",
    "axes[1].pie(\n",
    "    target_pct.values,\n",
    "    labels=[f\"{v}\\n({p:.1f}%)\" for v, p in zip(target_pct.index, target_pct.values)],\n",
    "    colors=[\"steelblue\", \"tomato\"],\n",
    "    startangle=90,\n",
    ")\n",
    "axes[1].set_title(\"割合\")\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.suptitle(\"ターゲット変数の分布\", fontsize=14, y=1.02)\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 数値変数の分布\n",
    "\n",
    "**確認ポイント**:\n",
    "- 正規分布か、歪んでいるか（歪んでいる場合は対数変換が有効なことがある）\n",
    "- 外れ値が存在するか（クリッピングや Winsorize が必要か）\n",
    "- ターゲット別に分布が異なるか（＝その特徴量が予測に効くかどうかのヒント）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ターゲットを 0/1 に変換（"Presence"/"Absence" 形式にも対応）\n",
    "y = train[TARGET_COL]\n",
    "if y.dtype == object or str(y.iloc[0]) in (\"Presence\", \"Absence\"):\n",
    "    y_binary = (y == \"Presence\").astype(int)\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    y_binary = y.astype(int)\n",
    "\n",
    "train_plot = train.copy()\n",
    "train_plot[\"target_label\"] = y_binary.map({0: \"Negative (0)\", 1: \"Positive (1)\"})\n",
    "\n",
    "# 数値変数だけ抽出\n",
    "num_cols = [c for c in FEATURE_NAMES if c in train.columns and pd.api.types.is_numeric_dtype(train[c])]\n",
    "print(f\"数値列: {num_cols}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 数値変数の基本統計量\n",
    "train[num_cols].describe().round(2)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ターゲット別ヒストグラム（分布の差がモデルの「手がかり」になる）\n",
    "n_cols = 3\n",
    "n_rows = (len(num_cols) + n_cols - 1) // n_cols\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(n_rows, n_cols, figsize=(14, n_rows * 3.5))\n",
    "axes = axes.flatten()\n",
    "\n",
    "for i, col in enumerate(num_cols):\n",
    "    for label, color in [(\"Negative (0)\", \"steelblue\"), (\"Positive (1)\", \"tomato\")]:\n",
    "        subset = train_plot[train_plot[\"target_label\"] == label][col].dropna()\n",
    "        axes[i].hist(subset, bins=30, alpha=0.6, label=label, color=color)\n",
    "    axes[i].set_title(col)\n",
    "    axes[i].legend(fontsize=8)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 余ったサブプロットを非表示\n",
    "for j in range(len(num_cols), len(axes)):\n",
    "    axes[j].set_visible(False)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.suptitle(\"数値変数の分布（ターゲット別）\", fontsize=14, y=1.01)\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Box plot: ターゲット別の箱ひげ図（外れ値も確認できる）\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(n_rows, n_cols, figsize=(14, n_rows * 3.5))\n",
    "axes = axes.flatten()\n",
    "\n",
    "for i, col in enumerate(num_cols):\n",
    "    sns.boxplot(\n",
    "        data=train_plot, x=\"target_label\", y=col,\n",
    "        palette=[\"steelblue\", \"tomato\"],\n",
    "        ax=axes[i]\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    axes[i].set_title(col)\n",
    "    axes[i].set_xlabel(\"\")\n",
    "\n",
    "for j in range(len(num_cols), len(axes)):\n",
    "    axes[j].set_visible(False)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.suptitle(\"数値変数の箱ひげ図（外れ値確認）\", fontsize=14, y=1.01)\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. カテゴリ変数の分布\n",
    "\n",
    "**確認ポイント**:\n",
    "- 各カテゴリの件数（極端に少ないカテゴリはモデルが学習しにくい）\n",
    "- カテゴリ別のターゲット陽性率（高低が大きいほどその特徴量が効く）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "cat_cols = [c for c in CATEGORICAL_LIKE if c in train.columns]\n",
    "print(f\"カテゴリ列: {cat_cols}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# カテゴリ別の件数 & ターゲット陽性率\n",
    "for col in cat_cols:\n",
    "    agg = train_plot.groupby(col)[\"target_label\"].apply(\n",
    "        lambda s: (s == \"Positive (1)\").mean() * 100\n",
    "    ).rename(\"陽性率(%)\").round(1)\n",
    "    cnt = train[col].value_counts().rename(\"件数\")\n",
    "    df_view = pd.concat([cnt, agg], axis=1).sort_index()\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n--- {col} ---\")\n",
    "    display(df_view)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# カテゴリ別 ターゲット陽性率の棒グラフ\n",
    "n_cols = 2\n",
    "n_rows = (len(cat_cols) + n_cols - 1) // n_cols\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(n_rows, n_cols, figsize=(14, n_rows * 3.5))\n",
    "axes = axes.flatten()\n",
    "\n",
    "for i, col in enumerate(cat_cols):\n",
    "    pos_rate = train_plot.groupby(col)[\"target_label\"].apply(\n",
    "        lambda s: (s == \"Positive (1)\").mean() * 100\n",
    "    ).sort_index()\n",
    "    pos_rate.plot(kind=\"bar\", ax=axes[i], color=\"tomato\", edgecolor=\"white\")\n",
    "    axes[i].set_title(f\"{col}\\n（カテゴリ別 陽性率）\")\n",
    "    axes[i].set_ylabel(\"陽性率(%)\")\n",
    "    axes[i].tick_params(axis=\"x\", rotation=0)\n",
    "    # 全体平均の水平線\n",
    "    axes[i].axhline(y_binary.mean() * 100, color=\"steelblue\", linestyle=\"--\", label=\"全体平均\")\n",
    "    axes[i].legend(fontsize=8)\n",
    "\n",
    "for j in range(len(cat_cols), len(axes)):\n",
    "    axes[j].set_visible(False)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.suptitle(\"カテゴリ変数別 ターゲット陽性率\", fontsize=14, y=1.01)\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. 相関ヒートマップ\n",
    "\n",
    "**確認ポイント**:\n",
    "- ターゲットと強く相関する特徴量（絶対値が大きいほど予測に効く）\n",
    "- 特徴量間の相関（相関が高い特徴量は情報が重複している可能性がある）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ターゲットを数値に変換して相関を計算\n",
    "corr_df = train[num_cols].copy()\n",
    "corr_df[TARGET_COL] = y_binary\n",
    "\n",
    "corr = corr_df.corr()\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 8))\n",
    "mask = np.triu(np.ones_like(corr, dtype=bool), k=1)  # 上三角を隠す\n",
    "sns.heatmap(\n",
    "    corr,\n",
    "    mask=mask,\n",
    "    annot=True,\n",
    "    fmt=\".2f\",\n",
    "    cmap=\"coolwarm\",\n",
    "    center=0,\n",
    "    vmin=-1,\n",
    "    vmax=1,\n",
    "    square=True,\n",
    "    ax=ax,\n",
    "    linewidths=0.5,\n",
    ")\n",
    "ax.set_title(\"特徴量間の相関ヒートマップ\", fontsize=14)\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ターゲットとの相関を降順で表示\n",
    "target_corr = corr[TARGET_COL].drop(TARGET_COL).abs().sort_values(ascending=False)\n",
    "print(\"ターゲットとの相関（絶対値, 降順）:\")\n",
    "print(target_corr.round(3))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. Train / Test の分布比較\n",
    "\n",
    "**なぜ重要か?**\n",
    "- Train と Test で分布が大きく異なると、Train で学習したモデルが Test で機能しない\n",
    "- これを **Covariate Shift** という。分布のズレがないかを確認する"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "n_rows = (len(num_cols) + n_cols - 1) // n_cols\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(n_rows, n_cols, figsize=(14, n_rows * 3.5))\n",
    "axes = axes.flatten()\n",
    "\n",
    "for i, col in enumerate(num_cols):\n",
    "    axes[i].hist(train[col].dropna(), bins=40, alpha=0.6, label=\"Train\", color=\"steelblue\", density=True)\n",
    "    axes[i].hist(test[col].dropna(), bins=40, alpha=0.6, label=\"Test\", color=\"orange\", density=True)\n",
    "    axes[i].set_title(col)\n",
    "    axes[i].legend(fontsize=8)\n",
    "\n",
    "for j in range(len(num_cols), len(axes)):\n",
    "    axes[j].set_visible(False)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.suptitle(\"Train vs Test の分布比較（数値変数）\", fontsize=14, y=1.01)\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 8. EDA まとめ・気づきメモ\n",
    "\n",
    "以下のセルに、EDA で気づいたことを自分の言葉でまとめてください。\n",
    "\n",
    "**テンプレート:**\n",
    "- **データ規模**: train __ 行 × __ 列、test __ 行\n",
    "- **欠損値**: （あれば列名と割合を記載）\n",
    "- **クラス不均衡**: Positive が約 __% → （問題あり / なし）\n",
    "- **予測に効きそうな特徴量**: （相関・分布差が大きかった列）\n",
    "- **外れ値が気になる列**: （Winsorize や対数変換の候補）\n",
    "- **次のアクション**: （前処理・特徴量エンジニアリングで試したいこと）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### メモ（自由記述）\n",
    "\n",
    "ここに自分の観察・仮説を書いてください。\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "*(例)*\n",
    "- データ規模: train 630,000 行 × 15 列、test 420,000 行\n",
    "- 欠損値: なし\n",
    "- クラス不均衡: Positive が約 55% → 大きな問題なし\n",
    "- 予測に効きそうな特徴量: Thallium, Number of vessels fluro（陽性率の差が大きい）\n",
    "- 外れ値が気になる列: Cholesterol（0 が多い？）, BP\n",
    "- 次のアクション: Cholesterol の 0 を NaN として中央値補完、ST depression の log 変換を試す"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 次のステップ\n",
    "\n",
    "EDA が終わったら次は前処理とベースラインモデルの作成です。\n",
    "\n",
    "1. `src/preprocessing.py` に欠損補完・型変換を実装する\n",
    "2. `src/train.py` を実行してベースラインスコアを確認する\n",
    "3. EDA で気づいた改善点を特徴量エンジニアリング（`src/features.py`）に反映する"
   ]
  }
 ],
